sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Src as Frame Source
  participant Pre as Preprocess
  participant Inf as YOLOv8 ONNX
  participant Post as NMS+Scale
  participant Trk as Tracker (IoU)
  participant Vel as Velocity
  participant Risk as Risk Engine
  participant Log as JSONL Logger
  participant Draw as Overlay
  participant Vid as Video Writer

  Src->>Pre: frame (BGR)
  Pre->>Inf: tensor (1x3x640x640)
  Inf->>Post: raw outputs
  Post->>Trk: det_list[{box, cls, conf, label}]
  Trk->>Vel: add velocity + confirmed + track_id
  Vel->>Risk: compute risk (confirmed only)
  Risk->>Log: write record (frame, infer_ms, dets, max_risk)
  Risk->>Draw: box color + text label
  Draw->>Vid: overlay frame
  Src->>Vid: raw frame (raw.mp4)
